}}'''伊塔乌文化学院'''（Instituto Itaú Cultural）是[[巴西|巴西]][[聖保羅_(巴西)|聖保羅]]一家[[非營利組織|非營利]]文化机构，由[[伊塔烏聯合銀行|伊塔烏聯合銀行]]所拥有<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://vejasp.abril.com.br/estabelecimento/itau-cultural-bela-vista/#|title=Itaú Cultural {{!}} VEJA SÃO PAULO|work=VEJA SÃO PAULO|accessdate=2017-11-30|language=pt-BR|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303123454/https://vejasp.abril.com.br/estabelecimento/itau-cultural-bela-vista/}}</ref>。该机构由奥拉沃·塞图巴尔（Olavo Setúbal）於1986年创建<ref>{{Cite web|title=lei Sarney – Lei 7505/86 {{!}} Lei no 7.505, de 2 de julho de 1986, Presidência da Republica|url=https://presrepublica.jusbrasil.com.br/legislacao/109576/lei-sarney-lei-7505-86|accessdate=2017-11-30|work=Jusbrasil|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914035223/https://presrepublica.jusbrasil.com.br/legislacao/109576/lei-sarney-lei-7505-86}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.pipaprize.com/2017/05/itau-cultural-celebrates-30-years-existence-constellation-brazilian-art/|title=Itaú Cultural celebrates 30 years of existence with a constellation of Brazilian art – PIPA Prize|date=26 May 2017|work=PIPA Prize|accessdate=2017-11-30|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225105518/https://www.pipaprize.com/2017/05/itau-cultural-celebrates-30-years-existence-constellation-brazilian-art/}}</ref>。该研究所有两个常设展览，分別展出歐洲人抵達巴西以來的巴西的绘画、素描、雕刻、地图以及[[葡屬巴西|葡屬巴西]]時期以來的金币和金条<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://epoca.globo.com/vida/noticia/2014/12/bhistoriab-contada-pela-arte.html|title=No Itaú Cultural, uma exposição conta a história do Brasil por meio da arte|work=revistaepoca.globo.com|accessdate=2017-11-30|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201042006/http://epoca.globo.com/vida/noticia/2014/12/bhistoriab-contada-pela-arte.html}}</ref>。

